auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"e1302b473dc12a9c8738646d7e909efc0f816946","tid":1743191,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"區選諗住投白票/廢票嘅人不妨睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81af124c327e70e87c2c7a2683e9603120dcd480","tid":1743191,"uid":338630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"推啊 至少革走啲獻世派啊"},{"pid":"6fcbad1a81765c2eec4d25967e9d64bc03b2b366","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"e59c26433456b1c164bd8bac01d69fe6035ed0c5","tid":1743191,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"區議會贏左又點, 都無用, 投唔投都罷啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1743208/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1743208/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6bd94d237c0188b8e9d506e05f9d015cf0c594ea","tid":1743191,"uid":209531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3307a9db4df20707eb3c42c162e43e80b33f3730","tid":1743191,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"11月24日區議會選舉其實係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變相公投</span></span><br />\n<br />\n公投d咩：咪就係撐政府，定反中共囉<br />\n點計票：數真藍票，同真黃票，仲有果堆不知名獨立人士，就會知道係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三分天下，還是二元對立</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">需唔需要努力確保區議會選舉順利?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔洗</span><br />\n<br />\n政府一直好努力想正常選舉，因為要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做比外國人睇香港係正常</span>。建制派就係一個condom，你死你事，唔關我事。<br />\n<br />\n平民都好想正常選舉，因為要拉班垃圾落台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">咁邊個最唔想選舉舉行?</span></span><br />\n咪就係condom 佢地囉<br />\n1：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">選舉失敗=建制派過去都失敗，中共會點睇呢班condom</span><br />\n2：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建制派除左做生意果批，民建聯有幾多無家底人士痴埋去做區議員，無左個位=失去生存能力</span><br />\n3：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以後無得claim咁多維穩費lu,辦事不力仲要claim咁多錢，short Q左啊你</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，手足們記得11月24日<br />\n記得早d去投票啊<br />\n<br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">印仔墨水乾左先好對接</span>入箱<br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">印仔一定要吸落圓圈範圍</span><br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要驗查張貼有無爛，有無印花左</span>"},{"pid":"858a6c66b0a2a24bd6a284a73e2a216611231c90","tid":1743191,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"1c71fa2a53c9abde027b38b3b0e3efbb6a93647f","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:11:42.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"9d61f69e231cd773387fc4a54ea38d43dbde4cdd","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"edf7f2fd6358f0b8586622eb09f73538abe5b783","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"3db9a3c67333d0e33cba0d090fcc15c724fb079c","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"c9544a3d444e60b417faddfcea8b9ae604c00e7c","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"34f1a736b564355e29f969bf5b9532b58d0a373e","tid":1743191,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"發揮非P牌超能力-推文回覆"},{"pid":"a880d4dff5989b65f21286b58f5192471c25c