<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6amePilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=b84a7344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6amePilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=d9a20f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/n</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期日0730 見)"},{"pid":"fc17992ed8e63d118c92e8348b434121c468275f","tid":1743191,"uid":274801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"213008cfc308be15ac4945159bf8a464907ed10c","tid":1743191,"uid":193538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"我嗰邊一個建制/一個泛民/一個垃圾! 一定唔好投白票! 唔會製造廢票!  唔好俾人吹風!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b93d0b04c8b789de2d6b7a95ed328b70c8dd5ce","tid":1743191,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca6a4f906013a79729cae28f55b6f1fe9e6a592c","tid":1743191,"uid":95409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"建制輸"},{"pid":"10574b94cf95401da4327cdb3acefa66872cc077","tid":1743191,"uid":185565,"lik